title: 2 people test positive for coronavirus in Srinagar, number of cases in J&K rise to 6
description: Two more people have tested positive for coronavirus in Srinagar, taking the total number of cases in the Union Territory of Jammu and Kashmir to six, a senior official said on Tuesday.
